p-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/009-research-backlog-remediation/006-review-registry-and-metadata-backfill/spec.md:\n  Line 26:     completion_pct: 0\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/011-followup-remediation/007-sliding-window-convergence-mode/spec.md:\n  Line 3: description: \"Implement ADR-001's opt-in sliding-window convergence mode to fix denominator drag in long deep-loop convergence scoring.\"\n\n  Line 11:     packet_pointer: \"deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/011-followup-remediation/007-sliding-window-convergence-mode\"\n\n  Line 14:     recent_action: \"Authored spec from ADR-001 (decision-record.md) sliding-window convergence design\"\n\n  Line 23:       session_id: \"sonnet-011-followup-remediation\"\n\n  Line 25:     completion_pct: 0\n\n\n(Results truncated. Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":100,"truncated":true},"title":"Status \\| In Progress|completion_pct: 0|completion_pct: 5|sliding-window|six of seven|6 of 7|011-followup","time":{"start":1782998440133,"end":1782998440161}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_074d2f22a48a93e6016a4665a7d2a4819185a618d4def40e77"}},"id":"prt_f22fd1835001U1NCcxPuDyeuhT","sessionID":"ses_0dd080809ffeSxS04s909esZ2m","messageID":"msg_f22fcbbf600107damhzSZvpul5"}}
