{"type":"text","timestamp":1782998691692,"sessionID":"ses_0dd080809ffeSxS04s909esZ2m","part":{"id":"prt_f23003fee001ml3WGi7I98z5Bf","messageID":"msg_f22fe8020001QCAViZCOABuJEx","sessionID":"ses_0dd080809ffeSxS04s909esZ2m","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n- Execute the detached deep-review fan-out lineage for `.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved` and write only lineage artifacts under `.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/review/lineages/gpt`.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- `artifact_dir` must be bound directly to `.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/review/lineages/gpt`; do **not** run `resolveArtifactRoot`.\n- Do not write outside `.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/review/lineages/gpt`.\n- `session_id=fanout-gpt-1782998103426-5a2g5w`.\n- `executor=cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast`.\n- `stopPolicy=max-iterations`, `maxIterations=10`, `convergenceThreshold=0.1`.\n- Run `phase_init`, `phase_main_loop` to 10 iterations, then `phase_synthesis`; convergence before 10 is telemetry only.\n- Final response must be exactly `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt`.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Loaded deep-review contract and related assets:\n  - `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md`\n  - `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_review_auto.yaml`\n  - loop/state references and templates.\n- Emitted PRE-BOUND setup bindings before writes.\n- Confirmed lineage dir is absent/empty: `.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/review/lineages/gpt`.\n- Read target root docs and key child/follow-up specs.\n- Investigated live code paths for fan-out prompt/session propagation, convergence, validation bridge, and tests.\n- No lineage artifacts have been written yet.\n\n### In Progress\n- Reviewing whether `deep_context_auto.yaml` / `deep_research_auto.yaml` actually satisfy the session-id propagation claims.\n- Checking validation bridge behavior around registry shell rules and strict-only rules.\n- Preparing phase-init artifacts and 10 iteration records.\n\n### Blocked\n- Spec Memory context loading is degraded:\n  - `E_SESSION_SCOPE`: `sessionId \"fanout-gpt-1782998103426-5a2g5w\" does not match a server-managed session...`\n  - `E_SESSION_SCOPE`: `sessionId \"memory-context:67444b8face5f43c\" is not bound to a corroborated server identity...`\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Treat this as a fresh lineage because the requested lineage artifact directory has no files.\n- Continue from on-disk packet evidence because Spec Memory MCP context failed.\n- Treat child `007-sliding-window-convergence-mode` as expected pending work unless evidence shows shipped-code claims contradict it.\n\n## Next Steps\n- Create only `.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/review/lineages/gpt` and `iterations/`.\n- Write `deep-review-config.json`, `deep-review-state.jsonl`, `deep-review-findings-registry.json`, `deep-review-strategy.md`, and `deep-review-dashboard.md`.\n- Write 10 iteration files with JSONL records, broadening angles each pass.\n- Update registry/strategy/dashboard after iterations.\n- Write `review-report.md` and synthesis/completion events.\n- Output `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt`.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Bound setup values already emitted:\n  - `review_target=.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved`\n  - `review_target_type=spec-folder`\n  - `review_dimensions=all`\n  - `execution_mode=AUTONOMOUS`\n  - `lineage_mode=auto`\n- Potential finding: root/phase metadata appears stale in places while changelogs say children `001-006` complete and `007` pending.\n- `deep_context_auto.yaml` grep showed `lineage.sessionId: \"{AUTO_SESSION_ID}\"`; verify against claim that review/research/context all propagate fan-out `session_id`.\n- `orchestrator.ts` calls `runRegistryShellRules(...)` at line 620; helper filters `rule.strict_only !== true && rule.severity !== 'skip'`.\n- `validator-registry.json` has `COMMENT_HYGIENE_MARKER` and `SCAFFOLD_NEVER_TOUCHED` as non-strict error rules; strict-only entries exist later.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/review/lineages/gpt`: only allowed output directory.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md`: workflow contract.\n- `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_review_auto.yaml`: review loop YAML and session/artifact binding.\n- `.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/spec.md`: target root spec.\n- `.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/011-followup-remediation/spec.md`: follow-up phase state.\n- `.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/011-followup-remediation/007-sliding-window-convergence-mode/tasks.md`: pending child evidence.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-run.cjs`: fan-out prompt/session source.\n- `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_context_auto.yaml`: session propagation check.\n- `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml`: session propagation check.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/convergence.cjs`: sliding-window convergence target.\n- `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/validation/orchestrator.ts`: validate.sh registry bridge.\n- `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/lib/validator-registry.json`: registry rule metadata.\n- `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/spec/validate.sh`: legacy validator behavior.","time":{"start":1782998646766,"end":1782998691691},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_087659ce60a8f6d3016a4666764dc4819aaeede03a3ec4f528","phase":"final_answer"}}}}
